### Development Setup

```bash
git clone https://github.com/blinkerbit/aird.git
cd aird
python -m venv venv
source venv/bin/activate  # Windows: venv\Scripts\activate
pip install -r requirements.txt
pip install -e .  # Install in development mode
```

